This directory contains utility functions for drawing
small directed or undirected networks.

Most of the code was written by Ali Taylan Cemgil,
SNN - University of Nijmegen, Department of Medical Physics and Biophysics
e-mail : cemgil@mbfys.kun.nl, 13-Apr-2000

The functions 'mkdot' and 'plotgraph', written by Kevin Murphy, are
wrappers to dotty, an excellent graph layout program written in C.
See http://www.research.att.com/sw/tools/graphviz for details.
